---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="The Open-Source AI Stack">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-12">
    <p
      class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-subtle)] mb-4"
    >
      A living map &middot; updated daily
    </p>
    <h1
      class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6"
    >
      The Open-Source AI Stack
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-prose mb-4"
    >
      Nine core layers, five cross-cuts, and the projects, news, grants,
      readings, and predictions flowing through each. A scheduled agent
      reads about thirty feeds once a day at 08:00 Pacific and routes
      each item to the layer it affects.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-subtle)] leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
      Click the bubble bottom-right to ask the in-site chat anything
      about what is on this site. Pure BYOK; add a key on{" "}
      <a href="/settings" class="no-underline hover:underline">settings</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <ul class="space-y-5 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] pt-8">
      <li>
        <a
          href="/stack"
          class="block group no-underline hover:no-underline"
        >
          <h2
            class="font-serif text-2xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-1"
          >
            The Stack &rarr;
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
            Fourteen layers from silicon up to protocols, with projects,
            news, grants, predictions, and reading lists at each.
          </p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="/grants"
          class="block group no-underline hover:no-underline"
        >
          <h2
            class="font-serif text-2xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-1"
          >
            Grants &rarr;
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
            Who funds open-source AI, what they actually fund, and the
            named gaps. Filterable by funder, layer, region, amount.
          </p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="/news"
          class="block group no-underline hover:no-underline"
        >
          <h2
            class="font-serif text-2xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-1"
          >
            News &rarr;
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
            Daily roundup, per layer. Auto-published once a day.
          </p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="/predictions"
          class="block group no-underline hover:no-underline"
        >
          <h2
            class="font-serif text-2xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-1"
          >
            Predictions &rarr;
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
            Falsifiable predictions per layer with horizons and
            resolution criteria.
          </p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="block group no-underline hover:no-underline"
        >
          <h2
            class="font-serif text-2xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-1"
          >
            About &rarr;
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
            How this site is built, the scheduled agent, the editorial
            and citation rules.
          </p>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
